
Capstone 2 specifications
Create an asset management system with the following specifications
1. Use laravel framework, but make not look like a laravel site
2. Asset functionality
	Add asset
	Retrieve assets
	Update assets
	Delete assets
	*Search assets
	*Filter assets
3. Transactions functionality
	Add asset to transaction
	View transaction
	Edit transaction item
	Delete transaction item
	Submit transaction request
4. Transaction history
	View history
	Admin: (approve or reject transaction, search transaction, filter transaction)
	User: (once transaction is approved, return assets to admin)
5. Other functionalities
	User login/registration 
	Dashboards for admin and catalog for regular user
	Authorization on pages
6. Project should be hosted in heroku and remotemysql
Bootcamp Dynamic Learning Environment